    </div>

    <div class="page" id="p12" style="background: #ffc2d1;">
        <h1 class="tw">Our Future üíç</h1>
        <p class="tw">I can't wait to grow old with you and see where life takes us.</p>
        <button class="btn" onclick="go(13)">Next ‚Üí</button>
